    "title": "Walk-in Drive Category Manager at Plum Holdings Services",
    "description": "Join the Plum Holdings Services family as a Category Manager in Delhi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Plum Holdings Services:\nPlum Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Plum Holdings Services!",
